headline: 3 Reasons We’re Fans of Elevance Health (ELV)
summary: Elevance Health trades at $423.06 per share and has stayed right on track with the overall market, losing 14% over the last six months while the S&P 500 is down 14.2%. This was partly driven by its softer quarterly results and might have investors contemplating their next move.
